highlights.text: “Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 229 weeks straight.
“Dinero” by Trinidad Cardona is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 28 spots at #33.
“Fiel - Remix” by Wisin, Jhayco, Anuel AA, Los Legendarios, and Myke Towers is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #29.
Olivia Rodrigo has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “good 4 u” is the highest at #1.
